{
  "stem": "2684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but soccer was the-- the sport in-- in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And study-wise, we had-- [LAUGHS] I know the nastiness started because we had a-- a-- a gymnastic teacher, or what we called PH-- PE-- PE teacher-- who came to the classes with a jackboots and the army uniform.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was nasty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But those-- those days, I-- I-- I didn't notice that he was only nasty towards Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was nasty to anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he made us to clean his boots, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sometimes he might call Jew boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would lie if I could remember that well that-- by what name he called me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] I has a funny experience, because he knew that my parents has poultry shop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he always ask me, any-- any good stuff came into the shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Go and bring me some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I could skip out-- classes, which didn't [? convient ?] me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was-- he didn't pay for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know whether my parents bought his-- his manner towards me better than towards somebody else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was hitting us, and-- and whatever those days the school teacher was doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, he turned to be-- and I heard that-- that they killed him during the war, because he became one of the nastiest, one of the most vicious anti-Semite in-- in our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were there any attempts made by your family to leave Hungary?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was made when I was very young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I only heard from my father that we had a-- a-- a close relatives in Hollywood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a very famous Hollywood actress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her name was Gaal Franciska.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
